Billion Dollar Secret



Company Summary
Kopin Corp. is a manufacturer of gallium arsenide transistor products and miniature flat panel displays for wireless communications and portable consumer electronics.  The company's gallium arsenide heterojunction bipolar transistors are used to produce power amplifier circuits for wireless telephone handsets and gigabit circuits for fiber-optic and Internet data transmission.  Kopin's CyberDisplay family of ultra-small, high density imaging devices is designed for portable products including camcorders, digital cameras and wireless handsets.  (PRESS RELEASE)   

















 




















